*Mrtvi* su se okupili oko groblja. (The dead have gathered around the graveyard.)

Policija je našla *mrtve* osobe u kući. (The police have found dead people in the house.)

*Mrtva* priroda je najbolje oslikala najdublji smisao života. (Dead nature has best depicted the deepest meaning of life.)

Ona je posmatrala *mrtve* ribe u koritu. (She was watching the dead fish in the trough.)

*Mrtvima* se treba iskazati poštovanje. (Respect should be shown to the dead.)